      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
      "body" : "First of all, if they were wrong, it ought to be not too hard for you to create a test case that disproves the constant-time performance? Second, if you look at the source code for HashMap, it does not call equals() against each key in the map - only when the hashcodes are equal."
