    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>The guy above gave comparison for HashMap / HashSet vs. TreeMap / TreeSet.</p>\n\n<p>I will talk about ArrayList vs. LinkedList:</p>\n\n<p>ArrayList:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>O(1) <code>get()</code></li>\n<li>amortized O(1) <code>add()</code></li>\n<li>if you insert or delete an element in the middle using <code>ListIterator.add()</code> or <code>Iterator.remove()</code>, it will be O(n) to shift all the following elements </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>LinkedList:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>O(n) <code>get()</code></li>\n<li>O(1) <code>add()</code></li>\n<li>if you insert or delete an element in the middle using <code>ListIterator.add()</code> or <code>Iterator.remove()</code>, it will be O(1)</li>\n</ul>\n"
  }, {
